OL,3,CNorthern Ireland has tools for health
OL,4,Cservice reform, says international
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland has all the tools to
OL,8,Freform its health and social care
OL,9,Fservice, an international expert has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FProfessor Rafael Bengoa warned that
OL,13,Fstaying with the current model will
OL,14,Fsee the service swallowing up all the
OL,15,Fpublic money in 15 years.
OL,17,FHe returned to Northern Ireland this
OL,18,Fweek, eight years after his major
OL,19,Fblueprint for reforming health
OL,20,Fservices in the region.
