OL,7,FRecommendations from the 2016 report,
OL,8,FSystems, Not Structures: Changing
OL,9,FHealth And Social Care by a panel
OL,10,Fheaded by Prof Bengoa, were never
OL,11,Ffully implemented amid the collapse of
OL,12,Ftwo assemblies and the Covid-19
OL,13,Fpandemic.
OL,15,FAddressing a conference at La Mon
OL,16,FHotel on the outskirts of Belfast on
OL,17,FWednesday, Prof Bengoa said the
OL,18,Fprinciples in the report are still
OL,19,Fvalid.
