OL,3,CNorthern Ireland has tools for health
OL,4,Cservice reform, says international
OL,5,Cexpert
OL,7,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill,
OL,8,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,9,FPengelly, Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,10,Fand Agriculture and Environment
OL,11,FMinister Andrew Muir were among those
OL,12,Fin attendance along with health
OL,13,Fservice workers.
OL,15,FProf Bengoa said there needs to be a
OL,16,Fmanagement system for change, plans
OL,17,Fand clarity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
