OL,7,FHe said that technology, including AI,
OL,8,Fwill help in some aspects but said
OL,9,Fthere may need to be a tough decision
OL,10,Faround hospital expenditure.
OL,12,F"Nobody really knows how to do that so
OL,13,Fpeople are exploring how to do that
OL,14,Fsort of decision, but if we stay with
OL,15,Fthe previous model we are going to be
OL,16,Fusing all the public money in 15
OL,17,Fyears," he said.
OL,19,F"It's better to start taking, slowly
OL,20,Fand incrementally, decisions in
OL,21,Frelation to where the finances go."
