OL,7,FProf Bengoa said a strong centre is
OL,8,Fneeded, but "not micro-managing".
OL,10,F"People in my country, in Spain, are
OL,11,Fhaving a really hard time doing that
OL,12,Fbecause you think you are going to
OL,13,Flose budget control, but actually
OL,14,Fpeople below identify much better
OL,15,Fsolutions than you above, so little by
OL,16,Flittle you start learning from the
OL,17,Flocal successes," he said.
OL,19,FHe insisted Northern Ireland has the
OL,20,Ftools and the political leadership to
OL,21,Fcarry out reform.
