OL,7,F"The leadership is there, there is a
OL,8,Fsense of direction and why not then
OL,9,Ftake this moment to develop this for
OL,10,Fmore rapid change," he added.
OL,12,FMr Nesbitt said he believes Prof
OL,13,FBengoa's visit will make a real impact
OL,14,Fand welcomed that ministers
OL,15,Frepresenting all the Executive parties
OL,16,Fattended the event.
OL,18,FHe is set to publish a plan around
OL,19,Fhealth and social care reform in the
OL,20,Fcoming weeks.
