OL,7,F"Prof Bengoa's analysis hasn't really
OL,8,Fchanged and it's still valid, he gave
OL,9,Fus principles to work to that he would
OL,10,Fstill recommend," he said.
OL,12,F"It's not as if the report has sat on
OL,13,Fa shelf for eight years gathering dust
OL,14,Fbut it is a question of saying, we've
OL,15,Fdone some good things, let's now
OL,16,Ffinish the deal."
OL,18,FMr Nesbitt said he will not shy away
OL,19,Ffrom making difficult decisions.
